annotationA: Ribosomal protein L30, isoform B; Structural constituent of ribosome. It is involved in the biological process described with: peripheral nervous system development; mitotic spindle elongation; translation; growth; centrosome duplication; mitotic spindle organization
annotationB: 60S acidic ribosomal protein P0; Ribosomal protein P0 is the functional equivalent of E.coli protein L10; Belongs to the universal ribosomal protein uL10 family
